data.description: Motivated Seller is offering an additional $5000 towards buyers closing costs!    Charming Florida Living at 4307 Chinaberry Circle, Bradenton - Your Slice of Paradise Awaits!    Property Highlights:  Nestled in the sought-after Golf Course Community of the River Isles neighborhood, 4307 Chinaberry Road invites you to experience the essence of Florida living. Boasting 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this meticulously maintained residence spans 1100 square feet, featuring an open floor plan and a myriad of captivating features that will instantly capture your heart.  Recent updates include a new electric panel, a new hot water heater, and new ceiling fans in both bedrooms.      Coastal Kitchen Delight:  Embark on a culinary journey in this charming kitchen, a haven for both cooking enthusiasts and entertainers alike. Create unforgettable memories in a space designed for both functionality and style.    Outdoor Bliss:  Step into your private oasis! The backyard unfolds into an enclosed patio overlooking a tropical paradise, offering the perfect setting to watch birds, unwind, host gatherings, and bask in the warm Florida sunshine. Picture yourself sipping morning coffee or hosting a barbecue with loved ones in this serene space.    Tranquil Bedrooms:  Escape to the comfort of bedrooms designed for relaxation, complete with walk-in closets and ceiling fans. Each room is a retreat, seamlessly balancing style and tranquility.    Convenient Garage and Parking:  Enjoy the blend of convenience and functionality with a one-car garage and ample parking space in the extended driveway. Whether you have multiple vehicles or need extra storage, this property has you covered.    Ideal Location:  4307 Chinaberry Road is perfectly situated for your convenience, with proximity to shopping and restaurants. Revel in the serene residential setting while enjoying easy access to the vibrant amenities that Bradenton has to offer.    Make It Yours:  Seize the opportunity to call this charming house your home! Schedule a private showing, and turn your Florida dream into a reality.
